FIFTH THIRD BANCORP, et al., petitioners,
v.
John DUDENHOEFFER, et al. No. 12-751. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 13, 2013.

Case below, 692 F.3d 410.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit granted limited to Question 1 presented by the petition.
